DateTime-Event-MultiCron version 0.01
=====================================

The DateTime::Event::MultiCrom is an extension to the DateTime::Event::Cron
module, that allow to create a DateTime::Set from multiple cron scheduling
definitions.

It implements only a from_multicron method, that gets multiple cron
definitions and returns a single DateTime::Set.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  DateTime::Event::Cron

